column2: SELECT s.specObjID, s.objid, s.ra, s.dec, p.z AS photoz, p.zerr AS photoz_err, s.z AS specz, s.zerr AS specz_err, s.modelMag_r, s.modelMagErr_r, s.type as specType, q.type as photpType, q.petroRad_r, q.psfMag_r, q.psfMagErr_r, q.fiberMag_r, q.fiberMagErr_r, INTO mydb.data1 FROM SpecPhotoAll AS s JOIN photoObjAll AS q ON s.objid = q.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz AS p ON s.objid = p.objid
